{
  "text": "The Anderson-Darling test for normality was used to explore the distribution of all data [CITATION_1] . The GLM procedure of the SAS 9.1 software (SAS Institute Inc., Cary, NC, USA) was applied to determine the significance of fixed effects using the F-test.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "120541257"
